00:20:40.651 --> 00:20:41.451
(2018 Cho Na Jeong)

00:20:47.691 --> 00:20:48.692
That's not me.

00:20:48.959 --> 00:20:49.826
Let's go.

00:20:50.794 --> 00:20:52.929
What do you expect me to do
by telling me that now?

00:20:53.597 --> 00:20:55.065
If I get fired because of you,

00:20:55.065 --> 00:20:56.266
are you going to take responsibility?

00:20:59.736 --> 00:21:00.504
Na Jeong.

00:21:12.349 --> 00:21:13.617
Talk to me.

00:21:14.017 --> 00:21:15.552
Why did you talk to Na Jeong like that?

00:21:17.120 --> 00:21:18.455
You can't fool me.

00:21:18.822 --> 00:21:20.090
We've been friends for 20 years.

00:21:20.857 --> 00:21:22.926
If you're struggling, say so.
If you're upset, say so.

00:21:22.926 --> 00:21:24.161
Why can't you just say it?

00:21:25.028 --> 00:21:25.929
Exactly.

00:21:27.197 --> 00:21:27.998
What is it?

00:21:28.768 --> 00:21:31.668
Are you having trouble trying to conceive?

00:21:32.736 --> 00:21:33.570
Yeah.

00:21:35.839 --> 00:21:37.274
You have no idea how miserable it is...

00:21:37.274 --> 00:21:38.842
to sleep with your husband
just to make a baby.

00:21:39.843 --> 00:21:42.112
My mom's anxious to death,

00:21:42.713 --> 00:21:45.082
the in-laws subtly blame it on my age,

00:21:45.549 --> 00:21:47.284
and my husband's not cooperative at all.

00:21:48.919 --> 00:21:50.387
It's stressing me out.

00:21:51.288 --> 00:21:53.624
But you still want a baby?

00:21:56.159 --> 00:21:57.361
I'm 41.

00:21:58.028 --> 00:22:00.497
Wait a little
and I won't be able to even if I want one.

00:22:02.399 --> 00:22:03.600
What if I regret it?

00:22:06.937 --> 00:22:09.573
The Executive Director
personally asked me to do this.

00:22:09.573 --> 00:22:11.642
But the friend
who was supposed to be interviewed says...

00:22:11.642 --> 00:22:14.044
her kid got sick
and she can't come last minute.

00:22:14.044 --> 00:22:16.446
It's going on the news.
We can't just have anyone do it.

00:22:16.446 --> 00:22:18.849
How can I do that without any prep?

00:22:19.583 --> 00:22:22.919
And honestly,
I don't even look presentable.

00:22:22.919 --> 00:22:24.521
I don't even know the event's purpose.

00:22:25.355 --> 00:22:28.025
It's about hiring
career-interrupted women.

00:22:28.392 --> 00:22:30.861
Sorry. I don't think I can do it.

00:22:30.861 --> 00:22:31.828
But...

00:22:32.262 --> 00:22:33.363
the reporter says...

00:22:33.830 --> 00:22:35.799
their schedule overlapped,
so we have to do it now.

00:22:35.799 --> 00:22:37.067
But people haven't even arrived yet.

00:22:37.534 --> 00:22:40.637
If you don't help me,
I'll get fired for real.

00:22:44.875 --> 00:22:47.711
What made you sign up
for this hiring fair?

00:22:48.512 --> 00:22:51.448
I used to work as a show host,

00:22:51.448 --> 00:22:53.283
but I quit because of my kids...

00:22:53.283 --> 00:22:55.218
about six years ago.

00:22:55.852 --> 00:22:58.889
Raising kids and running the house,

00:22:58.889 --> 00:23:02.125
I realized people called my name
less and less.

00:23:02.926 --> 00:23:05.796
So I'm not just here to find a job.

00:23:06.029 --> 00:23:08.465
I want to live my life again.

00:23:08.732 --> 00:23:10.400
That's why I came.

00:23:15.539 --> 00:23:17.274
- Mom.
- Hey.

00:23:20.410 --> 00:23:21.511
Thanks, Cho Na Jeong.

00:23:22.312 --> 00:23:24.414
If not for you,
we might've lost a whole segment.

00:23:25.215 --> 00:23:26.149
You're welcome.

00:23:26.149 --> 00:23:27.684
All right, take care.

00:23:28.185 --> 00:23:29.019
Thanks.

00:23:30.253 --> 00:23:31.922
Take care, Na Jeong. Thank you.

00:23:31.922 --> 00:23:33.523
Great work, Na Jeong.

00:23:33.523 --> 00:23:34.558
Okay, let's go.

00:23:34.858 --> 00:23:37.928
Hold hands, Min Woo, Min Jun. Let's go.

00:23:38.095 --> 00:23:39.730
Let's ride the vroom-vroom home.

00:23:52.275 --> 00:23:54.378
(2018, Home Shopping Host of the Year
Cho Na Jeong)

00:23:59.783 --> 00:24:00.584
Let's go.

00:24:15.265 --> 00:24:16.199
Thanks.

00:24:16.199 --> 00:24:17.067
You're welcome.

