What will you do
when you suddenly need a lump sum?

00:25:43.887 --> 00:25:45.522
Did something happen today or what?

00:25:46.323 --> 00:25:48.659
You've been nagging
like an old woman all day.

00:25:48.659 --> 00:25:49.559
Me?

