00:59:42.092 --> 00:59:44.027
Don't you want to go back
to Sweet Home Shopping?

00:59:44.027 --> 00:59:45.462
Should I try applying there once more?

00:59:45.462 --> 00:59:47.998
Why would you go there?
Who'd welcome you?

00:59:47.998 --> 00:59:49.466
Do you not find me attractive anymore?

00:59:49.466 --> 00:59:51.635
Sorry, but I feel sick.

00:59:51.635 --> 00:59:52.703
Let's end this.

00:59:53.937 --> 00:59:55.639
I must've been insane.

00:59:55.639 --> 00:59:56.840
Totally insane.

00:59:56.840 --> 00:59:58.775
I told you to apply somewhere else,
not Sweet Home Shopping.

00:59:58.775 --> 01:00:01.278
Why exactly can't I apply there?

01:00:01.478 --> 01:00:03.547
It seems the interview date got moved.

01:00:04.114 --> 01:00:05.515
- Thank you.
- Good luck.

01:00:05.515 --> 01:00:07.484
The competition's so fierce.

